2. The portable disinfectant wipe system of claim 1, wherein the dispenser comprises:
a body member formed of a leak resistant material;
a perforated opening formed in a top surface of the body member;
a resealing strip coupled adjacent to the perforated opening; and
a cover assembly attached to the top surface of the body member and enclosing the perforated opening.

10. A portable disinfectant wipe system comprising:
a dispenser for holding disinfectant wipes, wherein the dispenser comprises:
a body member formed of a leak resistant material;
a perforated opening formed in a top surface of the body member;
a resealing strip coupled adjacent to the perforated opening; and
a cover assembly attached to the top surface of the body member and enclosing the perforated opening;

a plurality of disinfectant wipes contained within the dispenser; and.
an adhesive material attached to a rear surface of the dispenser, wherein the adhesive material is double side tape.
